Dialogue: 69,0:00:18.10,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:20.76,0:00:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Close yer eyes for a sec.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:23.90,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, hold on. Wha—
Dialogue: 69,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Ya can open 'em now.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:28.01,0:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you just do?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:29.85,0:00:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave ya a present!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't get it!
Dialogue: 69,0:00:33.07,0:00:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shinpei, how many years has it been since ya been home?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:36.76,0:00:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Let's see.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:38.39,0:00:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Since graduating middle school, so... two years?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:42.04,0:00:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No kiddin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'didn't even come back fer New Year's.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:47.36,0:00:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to everyone when ya get there.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 69,0:00:52.05,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio, aren't you...
Dialogue: 69,0:00:53.40,0:00:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 69,0:00:56.33,0:01:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei, don't forget to find me.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:02.37,0:01:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Mio, okay?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:08.38,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:01:16.05,0:01:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:01:25.08,0:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 69,0:01:26.08,0:01:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm so sorry! \NI-I didn't mean to—
Dialogue: 69,0:01:30.03,0:01:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:37.13,signs,,0,0,0,,{=0}{\move(840,235,971.55,235,22,2316)\fscx42\fscy42\frz-15.99\fax0.29\fnUrban Jungle\fsp3\c&H503523&\1a&H19&\blur1.01}Port Kada to Hitogashima
Dialogue: 69,0:01:37.71,0:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I almost lost my life because of that weird dream.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:45.17,0:01:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chill out.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:46.97,0:01:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-At times like this,
Dialogue: 69,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should take a step back and settle down.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:53.20,0:01:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was the first time I've ever been slapped.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:56.66,0:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, I've simmered down.
Dialogue: 69,0:01:58.86,0:02:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be arriving at Hitogashima momentarily.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:01.68,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:03.43,0:02:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wakayama City, Wakayama Prefecture.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's an island in the Kitan Strait, Hitogashima.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got a population of about 700.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The local specialties are yomogi mochi and preserved squid.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:16.99,0:02:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a tiny island supported by tourism and fishing.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:21.62,0:02:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been about two years since I've last been here.
Dialogue: 69,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came back for my childhood friend's...
Dialogue: 69,0:02:35.58,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kofune Ushio's funeral.
