Dialogue: 69,0:02:53.36,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Shin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 69,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are ya tired from yer long trip?!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:09.84,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're ya doin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:15.04,0:03:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little sweaty, so I thought I'd go fer a swim.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:19.49,0:03:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad you seem energetic at least.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kofune Mio is Ushio's little sister.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:28.32,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She just lost her older sister. \NShe can't possibly be fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:33.41,0:03:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Protect Mio," huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:36.87,0:03:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:38.57,0:03:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:41.79,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea's salty.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:52.74,0:03:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's Tokyo?
Dialogue: 69,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did ya go to Shibuya? Did ya?!
Dialogue: 69,0:03:55.77,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I didn't go out much.
Dialogue: 69,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I got snot on my towel...
Dialogue: 69,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need to know that!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:02.35,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How's the shop doin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:02.35,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. I want you to bring it.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's super busy!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:05.31,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You make most of your money during summer break, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:08.77,0:04:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's so many people I don't know now.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:12.10,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, lately, even the people I know seem like strangers sometimes.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:17.35,0:04:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:19.63,0:04:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are a lot of tourists at this time of year.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's up?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yer soundin' like a real Tokyo boy, Shin!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 69,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It really rubbed off on ya.
Dialogue: 69,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're kidding!
Dialogue: 69,0:04:35.51,0:04:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We chatted about random stuff along the way to the funeral.
