Dialogue: 69,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I lost my parents ten years ago,
Dialogue: 69,0:06:25.51,0:06:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}so the Kofune family took me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.17,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Goodbye, Summer Days
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.87,0:06:27.17,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Goodbye, Summer Days
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.38,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\bord7\c&HC0A038&\blur7}Goodbye, Summer Days
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.38,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Goodbye, Summer Days
Dialogue: 69,0:06:29.25,0:06:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}So to me, not only is Ushio\N my childhood friend,
Dialogue: 69,0:06:32.98,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}she's also family.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:35.60,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day before I left the island, Ushio said she wanted me to make her curry.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I said "Maybe next time," and blew her off.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there never was a next time.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The poor thing.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it must be hard for Shinpei, too.
Dialogue: 69,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did ya hear?
Dialogue: 69,0:06:56.64,0:07:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hishigata performed an autopsy on Ushio's body!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,An autopsy?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:03.12,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's just plum outrageous!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did that? No photos.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:11.04,0:07:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A flash?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya finally came back, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:07:16.73,0:07:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio...
Dialogue: 69,0:07:20.15,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She tried savin' a kid from drownin', and... got swept away!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I was there, but she...
Dialogue: 69,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and...
Dialogue: 69,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,hit me until ya feel better!
Dialogue: 69,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's done is done.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:44.05,0:07:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, with everyone crying, it actually makes it easier to remain calm.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shinpei...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.13,signs,,0,0,0,,{=3}{\move(505,821,505,1146.9,21,2607)\frz4.75\fax-0.07\fnIgnite the Light\fsp2\xshad-3\yshad-3\c&HE5E7E7&\blur1.1}Hitogashima Hall
Dialogue: 69,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sou.
Dialogue: 69,0:07:55.92,0:08:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard your dad performed an autopsy on Ushio.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio died in an accident at sea, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at her.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:09.14,0:08:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Kobayakawa Shiori, man.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:11.17,0:08:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, from Koba Mart?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:13.02,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Man, she sure grew up.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in third grade now.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said earlier?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:20.36,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid Ushio saved was none other than Shiori there.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:26.97,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor girl.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:28.90,0:08:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't said a word since the accident due to the shock.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 69,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for the procession.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:42.56,0:08:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:44.68,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you lend a hand?
Dialogue: 69,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 69,0:08:48.00,0:08:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a call tonight. \NYou'll get the details then.
