Dialogue: 69,0:09:18.68,0:09:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm back so late, Shinpei.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Alan.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:24.89,0:09:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Karikiri sure loves his speeches.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:29.09,0:09:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, y'should be lendin' a hand!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:32.85,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My expertise is eatin'!
Dialogue: 69,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:37.65,0:09:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure smells nice.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:39.31,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Ushio's favorite dish, ain't it?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, could you set the table?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:44.90,0:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a serving for her too, huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've had your curry, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassa matter, Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:19.54,0:10:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha starin' at yer own house for?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya get in a fight or somethin'?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.16,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.41,title,,0,0,0,,{\bord5\c&HB69432&\blur7}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.95,0:10:32.41,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}Summer Time Rendering
Dialogue: 69,0:10:35.25,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:38.01,0:10:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why the autopsy?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 69,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was just the rumor mill getting out of control.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't open her up.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:46.75,0:10:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad was just there for the police's inquest.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that all?
Dialogue: 69,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 69,0:10:53.76,0:10:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,they found marks on Ushio's neck.
Dialogue: 69,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Marks?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:01.35,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like someone strangled her.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:04.95,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's possible this was murder!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:13.97,0:11:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, we were playing on the beach behind the elementary school since the tourists don't go there.{check for 3-line}
Dialogue: 69,0:11:20.74,0:11:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shiori was drowning and getting swept away, \NUshio was the first to notice and went to save her.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio and I jumped in right after.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there wasn't anyone suspicious around.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everyone know about the marks?
Dialogue: 69,0:11:33.80,0:11:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 69,0:11:34.96,0:11:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Only Mio, Mr. Alan, the police...\Nme, and my dad know.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:40.81,0:11:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But judging from the situation, it couldn't have been murder.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The police labeled it an accident. And that was that.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:49.34,0:11:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:01.51,0:12:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:02.83,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the necklace Sis was wearin' in her last moments.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:09.99,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should probably hold on to it.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio had this?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey—
Dialogue: 69,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 69,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,At least dry yourself off first...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:24.38,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm never...
Dialogue: 69,0:12:35.80,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,gonna... see her again!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:44.27,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:12:48.25,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive the one who killed her!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know something?!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:03.34,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You little!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:05.41,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:07.03,0:13:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothin'.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have the bath next.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:11.70,0:13:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis would get mad if she saw me crying like this.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's the last day I shed a tear!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty.
Dialogue: 69,0:13:37.61,0:13:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:39.65,0:13:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! I'll treasure it!
Dialogue: 69,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She still had this...
