Dialogue: 69,0:14:11.25,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The best thing to distract yourself from loss is to keep your body moving.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:16.68,0:14:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's probably what Alan and Mio were thinking.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:20.21,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And me too.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:22.01,0:14:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:23.69,0:14:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:24.81,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Didja find who yew were lookin' fer?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who was I looking for?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya told me when we met this mornin'!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:32.87,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,'Member? Y'said she was wearin' glasses and had huge honkers!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that really me?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:41.32,0:14:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to be drinking this much, Nakamura.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome in!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:46.20,0:14:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it is {\i1}scorchin'{\i0}!
Dialogue: 69,0:14:50.33,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the usual, please.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:53.08,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what's with today?
Dialogue: 69,0:14:57.63,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy is Totsumura Tetsu.
Dialogue: 69,0:14:59.89,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's a relative of the Kofune's, and he's the island's only police officer.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... "the usual," right?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:10.29,0:15:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What the? If it ain't Shinpei!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:12.36,0:15:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That stuff about Ushio... \NWhat do I even say?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:15.62,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Tetsu!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:17.52,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio! Still cute as ever, I see!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:20.04,0:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual B Lunch Set with an order of fried shrimp and medium-sized rice, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya got it!
Dialogue: 69,0:15:26.39,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to ya this mornin'?\NYa didn't come to eat breakfast.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:30.84,0:15:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. Get a load of this.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally crazy! Y'see...
Dialogue: 69,0:15:36.54,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kobayakawas have all vanished.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:42.18,0:15:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Kobaya...
Dialogue: 69,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kobayakawa Shiori.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:45.76,0:15:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The kid Ushio saved was none other than her...
Dialogue: 69,0:15:50.10,0:15:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Vanished?
Dialogue: 69,0:15:51.76,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, Koba Mart wasn't open at 8 AM.
Dialogue: 69,0:15:55.70,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So their neighbor, Shiomi's wife, took a peek into the main house and...
Dialogue: 69,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,it was completely vacant inside!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:05.09,0:16:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like they had quite a debt built up.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they ran off in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:14.98,0:16:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:16:19.06,0:16:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya going?!
