Dialogue: 69,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird that they came to the funeral yesterday.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kobayakawas.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 69,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the shop.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiori's been a bit off lately.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:05.72,0:17:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, she's mute from the shock, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:09.68,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:11.76,0:17:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, maybe a week before, she said somethin' weird.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:16.81,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when she was bug hunting on Mt. Takanosu. She saw...
Dialogue: 69,0:17:21.88,0:17:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl who looked just like herself.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:30.88,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, whether she was on her way to school or in school,
Dialogue: 69,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,she constantly felt like she was being watched.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:38.29,0:17:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that mean? Like a doppelganger maybe?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:42.16,0:17:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,'Scuse me. Ain't that the Shadow?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Nezu. He's a hunter.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:53.46,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it the shadow sickness.
Dialogue: 69,0:17:57.22,0:17:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow?
Dialogue: 69,0:17:58.52,0:18:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a disease endemic to this island.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:02.95,0:18:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not many have seen it in recent times, but it was quite common before the war.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:11.57,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If y'were taken with the shadow sickness, \Nyou'd start seein' yer "Shadow."
Dialogue: 69,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who saw their Shadow died.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They were killed by their Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:22.66,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And it pretends to be who it killed, \Nthen it kills everyone it lives with.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Least accordin' to legend.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:32.53,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So the afflicted would go to Hiruko to be cleansed.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:38.20,0:18:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my gramps used to say.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:41.83,0:18:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shin.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:47.05,0:18:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandma told me the same story when I was little.
Dialogue: 69,0:18:51.82,0:18:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the Shadow story before?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:54.77,0:18:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but... it's just a superstition, right?
Dialogue: 69,0:18:58.70,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it should be. \NBut I saw Sis' Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:06.47,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was three days before she passed.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:08.88,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We were picking up trash at Omoto Beach with a bunch of others.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:17.45,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Mio.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:20.90,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! \NIf that's a joke, I'm not laughing!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:27.82,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it disappeared right before our eyes!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:32.51,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, three days later, she...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Shiori's family...
Dialogue: 69,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 69,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calm down. Calm down!
Dialogue: 69,0:19:46.24,0:19:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, have you told anyone else about this?
Dialogue: 69,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to never crying again?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:02.68,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Hiruko and ask about the Shadow.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:08.68,0:20:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the old man said, right? \NThe cleansing and stuff.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 69,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin...
Dialogue: 69,0:20:25.26,0:20:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hiruko is the nickname for the \NHito Shrine in the northern part of the island.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No answer.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:50.71,0:20:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they out?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check out the worship hall.
Dialogue: 69,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 69,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:03.99,0:21:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you see that?!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:06.84,0:21:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not clearly...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:08.55,0:21:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear that was Shiori just now.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:11.26,0:21:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go after her!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:13.08,0:21:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:24.53,0:21:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothin'...
Dialogue: 69,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Could she be even deeper in?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:28.49,0:21:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Up ahead is the abandoned fort. \NIt's dangerous to go in there.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio, let's take a step back and think.
Dialogue: 69,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! Shin's "take a step back"!
Dialogue: 69,0:21:37.32,0:21:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Assuming that was Shiori, why'd she run from us?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why would she?
Dialogue: 69,0:21:45.94,0:21:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A gunshot?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's the one from the boat.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shin! What're you spacing out for?!
Dialogue: 69,0:22:13.82,0:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She's bleeding! Look! Look!
Dialogue: 69,0:22:15.56,0:22:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 69,0:22:16.58,0:22:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What do we do? \NWhat do we do, Shin?
Dialogue: 69,0:22:18.76,0:22:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:20.94,0:22:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go get someone!
Dialogue: 69,0:22:22.23,0:22:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Mio!
Dialogue: 69,0:22:25.38,0:22:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen closely... to me...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:29.85,0:22:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh... She...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:41.40,0:22:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's always sayin'...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:47.50,0:22:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shin...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:50.28,0:22:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That until you wash the dishes and clean everythin' up...
Dialogue: 69,0:22:56.08,0:22:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,service ain't over, y'know?
Dialogue: 69,0:23:15.33,0:23:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushio!
Dialogue: 69,0:23:20.94,0:23:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 69,0:23:25.93,0:23:25.93,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 5,0:23:44.32,0:23:47.33,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Since I remember it all
Dialogue: 5,0:23:48.29,0:23:51.08,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I'll alter my existence
Dialogue: 5,0:23:51.08,0:23:53.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Take a breath, take a breath
Dialogue: 5,0:23:53.92,0:23:58.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}The smell of a tepid tide, a choir of cicadas
Dialogue: 5,0:23:58.88,0:24:04.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's not something that can be forgotten
Dialogue: 5,0:24:04.30,0:24:09.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}Being torn by engulfing regret is best avoided
Dialogue: 5,0:24:09.81,0:24:14.40,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}So we're setting our lives aflame
Dialogue: 5,0:24:15.61,0:24:25.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}I can go on living just from the warmth of your palm if it's linked with mine
Dialogue: 5,0:24:26.53,0:24:37.38,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}What will be left remaining of this all too short summer I wonder
Dialogue: 5,0:24:37.38,0:24:43.88,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,200)}It's once in a lifetime, so we want to undergo a change
Dialogue: 5,0:24:43.88,0:24:48.81,ED,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(200,2000)}We want to change
